  },
  {
    "row": 114,
    "rowsha": "tq8T3GYsRt59cBFfiBUlMYAF6QuQbMy5Cema3daeeAE=",
    "originContent": "### Trimmer Command API",
    "translatedContent": "| ---------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ | ------------------------- |"
  },
  {
    "row": 115,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "| `trimmer`                          | 修剪每行末尾的空白                                                                                      | 整个文件                   |"
  },
  {
    "row": 116,
    "rowsha": "e19KISne9hmH2NEUIFIz7tWp/H23Y1YfX3FTLaW/wws=",
    "originContent": "| Command                            | Description                                                                                            | Context                   |",
    "translatedContent": "| `trim_leading_whitespace`          | 修剪每行开头的空白                                                                                      | 选区或整个文件             |"
  },
  {
    "row": 117,
    "rowsha": "KXaiHUXpoBInhovk+llWeg0mcCxeY6jmuYp8U3Kv+AU=",
    "originContent": "| ---------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ | ------------------------- |",
    "translatedContent": "| `trim_leading_trailing_whitespace` | 修剪每行开头和末尾的空白                                                                                | 选区或整个文件             |"
  },
  {
    "row": 118,
    "rowsha": "OPl8jZQrL8dk6aTCo1LhVAbn36aDxlFJ1irOLGx5TvM=",
    "originContent": "| `trimmer`                          | trim whitespace at the end of each line                                                                | entire file               |",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 119,
    "rowsha": "5VNqi2a3nfdhczwL9KVXtNXRR1Rvv4J1qZDXqBgiqQA=",
    "originContent": "| `trim_leading_whitespace`          | trim whitespace at the start of each line                                                              | selection, or entire file |",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 120,
    "rowsha": "A8FuNKT+jILAYADNQQX5ISfRMwD1vpqLzLNwMCw+pHI=",
    "originContent": "| `trim_leading_trailing_whitespace` | trim whitespace at the start and end of each line                                                      | selection, or entire file |",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 121,
    "rowsha": "KB+THLbIl2K/BlFe6ZVjqRWYFvGu7Z+DWRjcPoVpcAE=",
    "originContent": "| `trim_selections`                  | trim whitespace from selection(s)                                                                      | selection                 |",
    "translatedContent": "| `trim_selections`                  | 从选区修剪空白字符                                                                              | 选区                     |"
  },
  {
    "row": 122,
    "rowsha": "2OSdwF8tlIco0RsiGxm8JyJMneN9JWmFNa3AvvaknLI=",
    "originContent": "| `delete_empty_lines`               | delete empty, whitespace only lines                                                                    | selection, or entire file |",
    "translatedContent": "| `delete_empty_lines`               | 删除空行，仅含空白字符的行                                                                      | 选区，或整个文件          |"
  },
  {
    "row": 123,
    "rowsha": "p6T0UCmfXHTU85DC8+dZCVbH3QivbTcJpojiBeApaVw=",
    "originContent": "| `collapse_lines`                   | collapse multiple consecutive empty lines into one empty line                                          | selection, or entire file |",
    "translatedContent": "| `collapse_lines`                   | 将多个连续空行合并为一个空行                                                                    | 选区，或整个文件          |"
  },
  {
    "row": 124,
    "rowsha": "f1mZUnSwa4Lcs4sNz7lPC2ssKls4IDxp84zoptkp+tQ=",
    "originContent": "| `collapse_spaces`                  | collapse multiple consecutive spaces into one space                                                    | selection, or entire file |",
    "translatedContent": "| `collapse_spaces`                  | 将多个连续空格合并为一个空格                                                                    | 选区，或整个文件          |"
  },
  {
    "row": 125,
    "rowsha": "fVT/Jn1od92d73R6MqMA4gUckwq6xuclo0ge8kzKdWI=",
    "originContent": "| `trim_edges`                       | trim empty, whitespace only lines at the beginning and end of the file                                 | entire file               |",
    "translatedContent": "| `trim_edges`                       | 修剪文件开头和结尾的空行，仅含空白字符的行                                                    | 整个文件                  |"
  },
  {
    "row": 126,
    "rowsha": "HJrM7UkPUXgS6ztYetkDaodEDGWDb5nUlDqvqyRC7Pw=",
    "originContent": "| `remove_blank_spaces`              | remove all blank space characters (tab, cr, ff, vt, space)                                             | selection, or entire file |",
    "translatedContent": "| `remove_blank_spaces`              | 移除所有空白字符（制表符、回车符、换页符、垂直制表符、空格）                                  | 选区，或整个文件          |"
  },
  {
    "row": 127,
    "rowsha": "OQBO+EpcprDyEMRwM3fEh1iFsQY9h1A0mJQMOEE7xZc=",
    "originContent": "| `normalize_spaces`                 | consecutive spaces reduced, empty lines removed and lines trimmed                                      | selection, or entire file |",
    "translatedContent": "| `normalize_spaces`                 | 连续空格缩减，删除空行，行首尾修剪                                                              | 选区，或整个文件          |"
  },
  {
    "row": 128,
    "rowsha": "vquXsiEx4qB43tqv18GRU87yG3LbK9wMyJTuqGsuijI=",
    "originContent": "| `replace_smart_characters`         | replace smart characters (smart quotes, em/en dash, ellipsis, nbsp)                                    | selection, or entire file |",
    "translatedContent": "| `replace_smart_characters`         | 替换智能字符（智能引号、长短破折号、省略号、不间断空格）                                        | 选区，或整个文件          |"
  },
  {
    "row": 129,
    "rowsha": "DxCzN2zn9n+F05wXPS0yJOj8dz3hHYywcvsN8t0vfd4=",
    "originContent": "| `tokenize_string`                  | convert a string to a token by collapsing consecutive spaces, and trimming leading and trailing spaces | selection, or entire file |",
    "translatedContent": "| `tokenize_string`                  | 通过合并连续空格并修剪首尾空白，将字符串转换为标记                                            | 选区，或整个文件          |"
  },
  {
    "row": 130,
    "rowsha": "pawFHgY0vfk4wCZBzz4UkRXRUAiNpL3tdXZxLsWo40w=",
    "originContent": "| `delete_empty_tags`                | delete empty, whitespace only html and xml tags                                                        | selection, or entire file |",
    "translatedContent": "| `delete_empty_tags`                | 删除空的，仅含空白字符的 HTML 和 XML 标签                                                      | 选区，或整个文件          |"
  },
  {
    "row": 131,
    "rowsha": "o5gIERbRqq54wT3CrPy2TUIBfekxLEXcjcOcqt3S5e4=",
    "originContent": "| `remove_comments`                  | remove code comments and collapse lines                                                                | selection, or entire file |",
    "translatedContent": "| `remove_comments`                  | 移除代码注释并合并行                                                                            | 选区，或整个文件          |"
  },
  {
    "row": 132,
    "rowsha": "XIe7XOOwkw5Q+WEbQberioD/PiByCC/t0AJEiBq33yk=",
    "originContent": "| `delete_adjacent_duplicate_lines`  | delete adjacent duplicate lines                                                                        | selection, or entire file |",
